data.title: Zarqan Rural District
data.meta_description: Zarqan Rural District is in the Central District of Zarqan County, Fars province, Iran. It is administered from the city of Lapui.
data.text:
For the administrative division of Fars province, see Zarqan County. For the city, see Zarqan.

Zarqan Rural District (Persian: دهستان زرقان)[3] is in the Central District of Zarqan County, Fars province, Iran.[4] It is administered from the city of Lapui.[5]
